    <title>CentOS 7 安装Python 3</title>
    <url>/2019/03/14/centos-install-python3/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="CentOS-7-安装Python3"><a href="#CentOS-7-安装Python3" class="headerlink" title="CentOS 7 安装Python3"></a>CentOS 7 安装Python3</h2><blockquote>
<p>CentOS 7 默认值安装有Python 2.x 解释器，并不含有Python 3的解释器，需要单独安装</p>
</blockquote>
<a id="more"></a>

<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo yum update</span><br><span class="line">sudo yum install yum-utils</span><br><span class="line">sudo yum groupinstall development</span><br><span class="line">sudo yum install https:&#x2F;&#x2F;centos7.iuscommunity.org&#x2F;ius-release.rpm</span><br><span class="line">sudo yum install python36u</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
